===Noun===
'''whippersnapper'''
# a [[young]] and [[cheeky]] or [[presumptious]] person
#: (old man): ''These '''whippersnappers''', I don't know. They always want things [[immediately|right now]]: they can't seem to be able to wait for anything.''

